lter-neck-midaxi-beach-dress%2Fp%2Fclp60726889%3Fcolor%3DTOMATO\u0026amp;sref=https://www.theguardian.com/thefilter/2025/may/01/may-style-essentials\" data-link-name=\"in body link\" rel=\"sponsored\"\u003epure cotton halter neck midaxi beach dress (£39.50\u003c/a\u003e).\u003c/p\u003e\u003chr/\u003e\u003ch2 id=\"a-do-everything-shirt\"\u003eA do-everything shirt\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cfigure id=\"5c92ba32-7487-446f-9a5d-ed40c981bccb\" data-spacefinder-role=\"inline\" data-spacefinder-type=\"model.dotcomrendering.pageElements.ImageBlockElement\"\u003e\u003cdiv id=\"img-5\"\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource srcset=\"https://i.guim.co.uk/img/media/4e7184296ea5eeff25593b12f5d4ece34ab7c195/1000_0_3000_3000/master/3000.jpg?width=620\u0026amp;dpr=2\u0026amp;s=none\u0026amp;crop=none\" media=\"(min-width: 660px) and (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 1.25), (min-width: 660px) and (min-resolution: 120dpi)\"/\u003e\u003csource srcset=\"https://i.guim.co.uk/img/media/4e7184296ea5eeff25593b12f5d4ece34ab7c195/1000_0_3000_3000/master/3000.jpg?width=620\u0026amp;dpr=1\u0026amp;s=none\u0026amp;crop=none\" media=\"(min-width: 660px)\"/\u003e\u003csource srcset=\"https://i.guim.co.uk/img/media/4e7184296ea5eeff25593b12f5d4ece34ab7c195/1000_0_3000_3000/master/3000.jpg?width=605\u0026amp;dpr=2\u0026amp;s=none\u0026amp;crop=none\" media=\"(min-width: 480px) and (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 1.25), (min-width: 480px) and (min-resolution: 120dpi)\"/\u003e\u003csource srcset=\"https://i.guim.co.uk/img/media/4e7184296ea5eeff25593b12f5d4ece34ab7c195/1000_0_3000_3000/master/3000.jpg?width=605\u0026amp;dpr=1\u0026amp;s=none\u0026amp;crop=none\" media=\"(min-width: 480px)\"/\u003e\u003csource srcset=\"https://i.guim.co.uk/img/media/4e7184296ea5eeff25593b12f5d4ece34ab7c195/1000_0_3000_3000/master/3000.jpg?width=445\u0026amp;dpr=2\u0026amp;s=none\u0026amp;crop=none\" media=\"(min-width: 320px) and (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 1.25), (min-width: 320px) and (min-resolution: 120dpi)\"/\u003e\u003csource srcset=\"https://i.guim.co.uk/img/media/4e7184296ea5eeff25593b12f5d4ece34ab7c195/1000_0_3000_3000/master/3000.jpg?width=445\u0026amp;dpr=1\u0026amp;s=none\u0026amp;crop=none\" media=\"(min-width: 320px)\"/\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"John Lewis Stripe Cotton Shirt, Blue/Multi\" src=\"https://i.guim.co.uk/img/media/4e7184296ea5eeff25593b12f5d4ece34ab7c195/1000_0_3000_3000/master/3000.jpg?width=445\u0026amp;dpr=1\u0026amp;s=none\u0026amp;crop=none\" width=\"445\" height=\"445\" loading=\"lazy\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eStripe cotton shirt in blue\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://go.skimresources.com/?id=114047X1572903\u0026amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.johnlewis.com%2Fjohn-lewis-stripe-cotton-shirt-blue-multi%2Fp111801402\u0026amp;sref=https://www.theguardian.com/thefilter/2025/may/01/may-style-essentials\" data-link-name=\"in body link\" rel=\"sponsored\"\u003e\u003csub\u003e£45 at John Lewis\u003c/sub\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eOn the subject of holiday shopping, I’m seeing a whole lot of striped shirts being sold as “beach cover-ups”. I am all for the idea of a striped shirt as a beach cover-up, but I’m pretty sure you don’t need to buy a striped shirt specifically for this purpose. The striped shirt you already have in your wardrobe is perfect with jeans now (see number one, above) and – unbuttoned, with sleeves rolled up – on holiday, too. This blue John Lewis shirt is a great version if you are in the market for a classic.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure id=\"0967624c-e518-43fc-b182-bc34f4989f52\" data-spacefinder-role=\"richLink\" data-spacefinder-type=\"model.dotcomrendering.pageElements.RichLinkBlockElement\"\u003e\u003cgu-island name=\"RichLinkComponent\" priority=\"feature\" deferuntil=\"idle\" props=\"{\u0026#34;richLinkIndex\u0026#34;:27,\u0026#34;element\u0026#34;:{\u0026#34;_type\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;model.dotcomrendering.pageElements.RichLin